<keyLead id="B7144054FFA9FFB515DBF9FBB3ABF97A" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">
5. Style with poorly-developed angular subapical lobe (
<figureCitation id="94DEFFE4FFA9FFB51792F9FBB51DF944" box="[734,810,1658,1680]" captionStart="FIGURES 6" captionStartId="9.[151,264,1872,1896]" captionTargetBox="[167,1422,203,1835]" captionTargetId="figure-18@9.[151,1436,181,1849]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 6 A–F. Drabescus angulatus Signoret, male genitalia.A, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; B, valve and subgenital plates, dorsal view; C, style and connective, dorsal view; D, aedeagus, lateral view; E–F, aedeagus, dorsal and ventral views." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6479830" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6479830/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Fig. 6C</figureCitation>
); lateral processes of aedeagal shaft extending to top of aedeagus in ventral view (
<figureCitation id="94DEFFE4FFA9FFB51433F919B7F0F97A" box="[383,455,1688,1710]" captionStart="FIGURES 6" captionStartId="9.[151,264,1872,1896]" captionTargetBox="[167,1422,203,1835]" captionTargetId="figure-18@9.[151,1436,181,1849]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 6 A–F. Drabescus angulatus Signoret, male genitalia.A, pygofer and anal tube, lateral view; B, valve and subgenital plates, dorsal view; C, style and connective, dorsal view; D, aedeagus, lateral view; E–F, aedeagus, dorsal and ventral views." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6479830" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6479830/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Fig. 6F</figureCitation>
)............................................................... 
<taxonomicName id="CBE598E2FFA9FFB51185F919B3ABF97A" authority="Signoret" authorityName="Signoret" authorityYear="1880" box="[1225,1436,1688,1710]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Drabescus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="227" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angulatus">
<emphasis id="3E913F73FFA9FFB51185F919B372F979" box="[1225,1349,1688,1709]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">D. angulatus</emphasis>
Signoret
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0C5AE361FFA9FFB515DBF934B3AAF93C" blockId="2.[151,1437,1336,1944]" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">
<keyLead id="B7144054FFA9FFB515DBF934B3AAF93C" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">
