<keyLead id="B7144054FFA9FFB515DBF971B3AAF894" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">
6. Pronotum and mesonotum predominantly orange brown (Figs 1G–J); aedeagus including dorsal apodeme U-shaped, basal processes of shaft about 0.66 as long as shaft in lateral view (
<figureCitation id="94DEFFE4FFA9FFB51662F88CB54DF8F7" box="[814,890,1805,1827]" captionStart="FIGURES 8" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1899,1923]" captionTargetBox="[166,1420,193,1864]" captionTargetId="figure-28@16.[151,1436,181,1876]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 8 A–I. Drabescus kempi Pruthi, male genitalia. A, genital capsule, lateral view; B, pygofer, anal tube, valve and subgenital plate, lateral view; C, distal half of pygofer ventral view; D, valve and subgenital plate, dorsal view; F, aedeagus, lateral view;; G, styles, connective and aedeagus, dorsal view; H, aedeagus lateral view; style, I, connective and aedeagus, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6479836" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6479836/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Fig. 8H</figureCitation>
), in dorsal view weakly divergent from shaft (
<figureCitation id="94DEFFE4FFA9FFB51079F88CB347F8F7" box="[1333,1392,1805,1827]" captionStart="FIGURES 8" captionStartId="16.[151,264,1899,1923]" captionTargetBox="[166,1420,193,1864]" captionTargetId="figure-28@16.[151,1436,181,1876]" captionTargetPageId="16" captionText="FIGURES 8 A–I. Drabescus kempi Pruthi, male genitalia. A, genital capsule, lateral view; B, pygofer, anal tube, valve and subgenital plate, lateral view; C, distal half of pygofer ventral view; D, valve and subgenital plate, dorsal view; F, aedeagus, lateral view;; G, styles, connective and aedeagus, dorsal view; H, aedeagus lateral view; style, I, connective and aedeagus, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6479836" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6479836/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Figs 8</figureCitation>
EF)....................................................................................... 
