<figureCitation id="94DEFFE4FFA9FFB51673F8E4B54EF8AF" box="[831,889,1893,1915]" captionStart="FIGURES 7" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1911,1935]" captionTargetBox="[162,1423,197,1874]" captionTargetId="figure-18@15.[151,1436,181,1887]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 7A–H. Drabescus austroindicus sp. nov., male genitalia.A, male genital capsule, lateral view; B, pygofer, anal tube, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; C. distal half of pygofer, ventral view; D. valve and subgenital plates, dorsal view; E, styles, connective and aedeagus, dorsal view; F, connective and aedeagus, ventral view; G–H, aedeagus, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6479832" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6479832/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Fig. 7</figureCitation>
GH), in dorsal view strongly divergent from shaft (
<figureCitation id="94DEFFE4FFA9FFB5103EF8E4B6DAF84C" captionStart="FIGURES 7" captionStartId="15.[151,264,1911,1935]" captionTargetBox="[162,1423,197,1874]" captionTargetId="figure-18@15.[151,1436,181,1887]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURES 7A–H. Drabescus austroindicus sp. nov., male genitalia.A, male genital capsule, lateral view; B, pygofer, anal tube, valve and subgenital plates, lateral view; C. distal half of pygofer, ventral view; D. valve and subgenital plates, dorsal view; E, styles, connective and aedeagus, dorsal view; F, connective and aedeagus, ventral view; G–H, aedeagus, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6479832" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6479832/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="227">Figs 7</figureCitation>
EF)............................................................................ 
